snippet.title: Skyworld Kingdom Brawl - Fresh Meat DLC Trailer [ESRB]
snippet.description: Free DLC “Fresh Meat” launches Thursday, September 5, 2019! It will introduce 8 new units, 5 new maps, and a host of new tactical possibilities to destroy friendships in Skyworld: Kingdom Brawl.
